.survey-faq.note
  %h3 How will you use my data?

  :markdown
    Survey results will be used in aggregate to generate statistics on design budets.

    This data will then be used both inside Folyo and on the Folyo blog to help clients figure out appropriate budgets for their projects.

    Please note that all data collected here will remain **strictly anonymous**.
